# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
tfplan
plan.txt
crash.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Secrets - never commit real tfvars
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example

# Editors / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# Claude automation — local, per-user, secret-bearing
.claude/hooks/config.env
.claude/scripts/*.local.sh
# Never commit lab credentials dropped into the repo (data files only —
# the refresh *script* below is committed template code, not a secret)
*azure-lab-creds*.json
*azure-lab-creds*.env
*creds.env
!.claude/hooks/config.env.example
!.claude/scripts/azure-lab-creds.sh
